## Learning Journey 
### Learning Journey to MOE Heritage Centre 

What's Singapore's Education Story? Visit the Ministry of Education (MOE)'s Heritage Centre to understand the Singapore Education Story and its contribution towards nation-building. Through a guided tour, participants will visit every zone in the heritage gallery to explore a different era of education in Singapore. 

**Date and Time: 5 Jul 2019, 2.30pm to 4.00pm 
**Location: MOE Heritage Centre, 402 Commonwealth Drive, S(149599) 
**Indicate Your Interest [here](https://www.eventbrite.sg/e/step-into-my-shoes-making-a-difference-as-a-probation-officer-tickets-61082209533)** 

